### SCRIPT 2: `build_features.py` — Viết mới

**Nhiệm vụ**: Từ `cleaned_df` tạo ra đúng feature V1 theo công thức FE notebook Phase 3.

#### A. Payment/Order features

| Feature | Công thức | Nguồn |
|---|---|---|
| `is_cod` | `1 if payment_method == "COD" else 0` | `orders.payment_method` |
| `payment_method` | giữ nguyên string | `orders.payment_method` |
| `device_type` | giữ nguyên string | `orders.device_type` |
| `order_source` | giữ nguyên string | `orders.order_source` |
| `payment_value` | giữ nguyên float | `payments.payment_value` |
| `log_payment_value` | `np.log1p(payment_value)` | derived |

#### B. Customer features

| Feature | Công thức | Nguồn |
|---|---|---|
| `customer_tenure_days` | `(order_date - signup_date).dt.days` | orders + customers |
| `tenure_group` | pd.cut: <30, 30-180, 180-365, >365 days | derived |
| `age_group` | giữ nguyên string | `customers.age_group` |
| `gender` | giữ nguyên string | `customers.gender` |

#### C. Order item aggregate features

| Feature | Công thức | Nguồn |
|---|---|---|
| `total_quantity` | sum(quantity) per order | order_items aggregated |
| `unique_product_count` | count distinct product_id per order | order_items |
| `discount_ratio` | total_discount / total_gross_value (0 nếu gross=0) | derived |
| `is_discounted` | `1 if discount_ratio > 0 else 0` | derived |

#### D. Product descriptor multi-hot (per order, V1 only)

| Feature group | Values | Nguồn |
|---|---|---|
| `category_*` | Casual, GenZ, Outdoor, Streetwear | products.category join order_items |
| `segment_*` | Activewear, Balanced, Everyday, Performance, Premium, Standard | products.segment |
| `size_*` | L, M, S, XL | products.size |

> Multi-hot: nếu order có ít nhất 1 item thuộc value đó → 1, else → 0. Không dùng `color_*` (bị drop ở selection).

**Không tạo**: `payment_value_quantile_bucket`, banned features, calendar features (experimental), `payment_device_interaction` (experimental).

**Leakage gate**: Fail-fast nếu bất kỳ banned feature nào xuất hiện trong output.

